&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;BAND 5 STAFF NURSE Out-Patient Department&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;37.5 Hours per week&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; We are looking for an enthusiastic, caring nurse to join the Out-Patient department at the Queen Elizabeth Hospital in Gateshead on a 37.5 hour per week contract, over 5 working days, although part-time hours would be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We require a staff nurse who is going to help us continue the development of our service to provide an effective, safe service which is known for its friendly, helpful staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a multi-site, multi-speciality service and the post holder will be expected to work within a busy Fracture and Orthopaedic Department, Ent Services, Surgical services and Breast Screening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also provide clinics at Blaydon Health Centre, Grindon Health Centre and Washington Primary Health Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The postholder must therefore possess excellent communication and organisational skills, be able to demonstrate leadership skills, work as part of a team and demonstrate initiative and problem-solving skills. The postholders must also be able to plan their own work and work flexibly to meet the ever changing requirements of the service both within the department and Trust wide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a 1st Level Nurse with evidence of ongoing professional development.  Car owner/driver is essential as we are a multi-site service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you possess the qualities we are looking for, we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal visits/enquiries are very welcome. Please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
